# Git Attributes for Fairy Dinosaur Date Night
# =============================================
#
# IMPORTANT: Large binary files (images, video, audio, 3D models)
# are stored in Cloudflare R2, NOT in git.
#
# See CLAUDE.md for R2 storage instructions.
# R2 Public URL: https://pub-97d84d215bf5412b8f7d32e7b9047c54.r2.dev
#
# Only small text files and code should be committed to git.

# Explicitly exclude asset directories from LFS (they go to R2)
assets/** -filter
animatics/** -filter
storyboards/** -filter

# docs/images for GitHub Pages (small files only)
docs/images/** binary

# Keep text files as text
*.md text
*.py text
*.js text
*.html text
*.css text
*.json text
*.yaml text
*.yml text
*.sh text
